---
// /contact — 3 폼 탭을 클라이언트 필터로 분기 (§6.10 패턴)
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import ContactPageHead from "@/components/common/ContactPageHead.astro";
import FilterScript from "@/components/common/FilterScript.astro";
import ScrollToTop from "@/components/common/ScrollToTop.astro";
import InquiryForm from "@/components/forms/InquiryForm";

import { sanityClient } from "@/lib/sanity";
import { siteSettingsQuery } from "@/lib/queries";
import { pickLocale } from "@/types/sanity";
import type { SiteSettings } from "@/types/sanity";

const site = await sanityClient.fetch<SiteSettings | null>(siteSettingsQuery);

const WORKER_URL = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_WORKER_URL || "";
const TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY || "";

const FORMS = [
  {
    slug: "personal" as const,
    eyebrow: "Personal Consulting",
    title: "당신의 결을 시작합니다.",
  },
  {
    slug: "corporate" as const,
    eyebrow: "Corporate Inquiry",
    title: "임직원의 인상이, 회사의 결정입니다.",
  },
  {
    slug: "academy" as const,
    eyebrow: "Academy Enrollment",
    title: "수강 문의.",
  },
];

const envReady = WORKER_URL && TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY;
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact — CMK Image Korea"
  description="개인 컨설팅 · 기업 출강 · Academy 수강 문의"
>
  {/* Turnstile script — Contact 페이지에만 로드 */}
  <script
    is:inline
    src="https://challenges.cloudflare.com/turnstile/v0/api.js"
    async
    defer
    slot="head"
  />

  <ContactPageHead />

  <section class="bg-background">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[var(--container-max)] px-[var(--container-padding)] py-14 md:py-24">

      {!envReady && (
        <div class="mx-auto mb-12 max-w-2xl border border-accent bg-cream p-6 text-sm text-soft">
          <p class="font-semibold text-accent">⚠️ 폼이 비활성 상태입니다</p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            <code class="text-xs">PUBLIC_WORKER_URL</code> 또는
            <code class="text-xs">PUBLIC_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY</code> 환경변수가 비어 있습니다.
            Phase 4.5 사용자 액션 가이드를 확인하세요.
          </p>
        </div>
      )}

      <div data-filter-root>
        {FORMS.map((f) => (
          <div
            data-card
            data-form={f.slug}
            class:list={["mx-auto max-w-4xl", f.slug !== "corporate" && "hidden"]}
          >
            <div class="mb-8 text-center">
              <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-muted">
                {f.eyebrow}
              </p>
              <h2 class="mt-4 font-serif italic text-3xl text-foreground">{f.title}</h2>
            </div>

            <InquiryForm
              kind={f.slug}
              workerUrl={WORKER_URL}
              turnstileSiteKey={TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY}
              client:visible
            />
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      {/* 회사 정보 */}
      <div class="mx-auto mt-24 grid max-w-3xl grid-cols-1 gap-8 border-t border-foreground pt-12 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-muted">
            Office
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-soft">
            {pickLocale(site?.companyName) || "CMK 이미지 코리아"}
          </p>
          {site?.address && (
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">{pickLocale(site.address)}</p>
          )}
          {site?.phone && <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted">{site.phone}</p>}
          {site?.email && (
            <a
              href={`mailto:${site.email}`}
              class="mt-1 block text-sm text-muted underline-offset-4 hover:text-accent hover:underline"
            >
              {site.email}
            </a>
          )}
        </div>

        <div>
          <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-muted">
            Follow
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-sm">
            {site?.instagram && <li><a href={site.instagram} class="text-muted hover:text-accent">Instagram →</a></li>}
            {site?.youtube && <li><a href={site.youtube} class="text-muted hover:text-accent">YouTube →</a></li>}
            {site?.facebook && <li><a href={site.facebook} class="text-muted hover:text-accent">Facebook →</a></li>}
            {site?.naverBlog && <li><a href={site.naverBlog} class="text-muted hover:text-accent">Naver Blog →</a></li>}
            {site?.kakaoChannel && <li><a href={site.kakaoChannel} class="text-muted hover:text-accent">Kakao →</a></li>}
            {!site?.instagram && !site?.youtube && !site?.facebook && !site?.naverBlog && !site?.kakaoChannel && (
              <li class="text-faint text-xs">[ SNS 링크 입력 시 자동 노출 ]</li>
            )}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <FilterScript filterKey="form" defaultValue="corporate" />
  <ScrollToTop />
</BaseLayout>
